HEADWORD: Chowchow
<hw>Chow"chow`</hw> <pr>(chou"chou`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Chin.]</ety> <def>Consisting of several kinds mingled together;
mixed; <as>as, <ex>chowchow</ex> sweetmeats (preserved fruits put
together)</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chow-chow</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chowchow
<hw>Chow"chow`</hw> <pr>(chou"chou`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>A kind of mixed pickles.</def>⟦br⟧
